<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Profile Card</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #cceeff; /* Light blue background */
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 350px;
            width: 90%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .name {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .about {
            font-size: 0.95em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .info {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="name">Turla, Francois B.</div>
        <div class="title">Assistant Developer</div>
        <div class="about">"Passionate about coding and problem-solving, I assist in developing efficient software solutions. Eager to learn and grow in the tech industry, I focus on teamwork and continuous improvement."</div>
        <div class="info">Age: 19</div>
        <div class="info">Email: coasturla@gmail.com</div>
        <div class="info">Contact: 09104307647</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html
